DEPENDENCIES
------------
Read docs/source/setup.rst to setup the environment.

RUNNING
-------
Ensure the PDK is installed into ~/tools/pdk.  Or else just change all instances
of ~/tools/pdk to your $PDK_ROOT.  (I could have made this easier for you to set
up but this is a lazy repository.)

To run and simulate everything:
    make

To view waveforms:
    ./view-inverter.py
    ./view.py <.dat file>
    ./view-transient.py inverter-testbench-curves.dat


